channel.title: Custom Items Get Nulled When Spawned
channel.description: Hey guys, I currently downloaded KingScape Client and ShortRide-Scape Source. Unlike other servers and clients this ran with no problem, nice and lagg free. The only problem I had was that when I try to spawn a custom item it shows up as a null. I have the customs added on the client...so am guessing this has something to do with the source? Also don't say that I have to click add models...because I've already done that. So if anybody good help me out, I'd really appreciate it.
